<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4271660>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 5. Phylogenetic relationships of Pithecopus Cope, 1866 based on 16S rDNA mitochondrial fragment. Topology inferred from the Bayesian inference based on the GTR+G model. Posterior probabilities are shown at each node. Scale bar represents the number of substitutions per site. Expanded topology for P. gonzagai sp. nov. and P. nordestinus (Caramaschi, 2006) is in Supplementary file 6." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4271660/files/figure.png" .

